{"tid":773907,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"深水埗居民填表入會換米　事後疑「被登記」做選民 (23:08)","createTime":"2018-08-10T01:58:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-10T04:28:20.000Z","uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d36ab039d5f333fecdbd3aa855aca60708013554","tid":773907,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-10T01:58:32.000Z","msg":"民協深水埗區議員楊彧在facebook表示，收到街坊投訴，登記成為香港廣西貴港市政協同鄉聯誼會會員後，疑有人利用個人資料，令他「被登記」做選民。<br />\n<br />\n楊彧稱，有建制派過去一個月在海麗邨內宣傳「入會換米」。只要有身分證，申請加入廣西貴港市政協同鄉聯誼會後，即可換3至5公斤米。他向本報表示，先後有兩名街坊向他表示，自己沒有登記做選民，但填完申請表、簽名加入聯誼會後，就收到選舉事務處選民登記確認信，懷疑對方利用他們的個人資料。<br />\n<br />\n依楊彧上載的入會申請表所見，申請人要填上姓名和出生日期，更要填上身分證號碼、住址等資料。楊認為是過度收集個人資料，呼籲市民留意。<br />\n<br />\n本報暫未聯絡到香港廣西貴港市政協同鄉聯誼會人士。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180809/s00001/38419c6bde46c39002814acc0d681773.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F38419c6bde46c39002814acc0d681773.jpg&h=30d29af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180809/s00001/38462639a58e251b9b21f3c6b36ed1da.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F38462639a58e251b9b21f3c6b36ed1da.jpg&h=f8627154&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180809/s00001/3848e280c7c8485750cb048d6d2b1d56.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F3848e280c7c8485750cb048d6d2b1d56.jpg&h=c906beea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180809/s00001/1533827288002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180809%2Fs00001%2F1533827288002&d=0QVthNlhK99TeRNrWxp4kEzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=cf3ec1b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F201808